\series default
 between agents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Decentralization is essential, because it would be extremely hard for a
 single player to solve the whole problem of the economy and find the equilibriu
a.
 An enormous amount of misinformation would have been involved, while in
 the decentralized case there is no risk of deception, because everyone
 solves a small bit of the puzzle.
\end_layout

