\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Consider 2 consumers with idential preferences, but opposite endowments.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It can be shown that the equilibrium is reached at 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\delta=\frac{1}{1+r}
\]

\end_inset


